title: For Sale/Trade:  HK P30LS V3 9mm DA/SA ambi safety & decocker
postcontent:
I have a Heckler & Koch P30LS V3 in 9mm that I am considering selling/trading. This is HK’s top-of-the-line dual action / single action pistol. It has a 4.5 inch barrel. It comes with two 15 round magazines.
This configuration is the best model ever offered, because it will run either dual action or single action, has an external ambidextrous safety AND a decocker next to the hammer. You can find an HK without the safety, or without the decocker, but ones that are loaded like this one, are rare.
It can be carried with one in the chamber and decocked, or condition one with safety on and hammer back.
The sights are glow-in-the dark white dot night sights, which actually glow for a long time.
This one comes with the original HK case, 2 magazines, the different thickness grip back straps and side straps. I am the second owner and have the original receipt for when it was purchased by the original owner.
When I purchased it from the original owner, it came with an inside the waistband holster which was purported to be for a Glock 20 I think, so the fit isn’t perfect and I never used it.
The Streamlight TLR-2 light/laser combo is not included unless negotiated into the deal.  I plan on keeping it but could be convinced to sell/trade as part of a package (don't want to sell separately)
I plan on attending the Washington Arms Collector Show this weekend and could meet there.  I don't need to sell this gun and won't sell it super cheap, and FFL transfer will be required

Browning Micro Midas firearms are designed specifically for smaller framed shooters. If you give a new shooter a long gun that is too large for them, they will develop bad habits in their form as they are doing everything they can just to hold the barrel up and get some kind of sight picture. The Micro Midas BPS shaves off weight and length (which can be adjusted with included stock spacers), creating a more compact and easy to handle package. The vented rib barrel and the forged, machined steel receiver are gloss blued.
